{"noun":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/04/5c/2766_crt_anidb.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/04/5c/2766_crt_anidb.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/04/5c/2766_crt_anidb.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/04/5c/2766_crt_anidb.jpg"},"name":"長峰美加子","summary":"","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"","grid":"","large":"","medium":""},"name":"篠原美香","short_summary":"","career":["seiyu"],"id":4527,"type":1,"locked":false},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/4e/f1/4589_seiyu_anidb.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/4e/f1/4589_seiyu_anidb.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/4e/f1/4589_seiyu_anidb.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/4e/f1/4589_seiyu_anidb.jpg"},"name":"武藤寿美","short_summary":"日本的女性配音员、演员。出身于东京都。已婚，丈夫为动画师冲浦启之。\r\n\r\n以前所属的经纪公司是剧团若草（1982年－1992年）、Liberta，现隶属于株式会社ALBA。早稻田大学第二文学部演剧学科毕业。\r\n为人熟悉的代表配音作品是电影导演冲浦启之执导动画《人狼 JIN-ROH》的雨宫圭和《星之声》的长峰美加子。\r\n兴趣是电影和音乐鉴赏、读书、散步。特技为日本舞蹈。","career":["seiyu"],"id":4589,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":2766},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/71/be/27785_crt_uuuH8.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/71/be/27785_crt_uuuH8.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/71/be/27785_crt_uuuH8.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/71/be/27785_crt_uuuH8.jpg"},"name":"寺尾昇","summary":"","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/1c/06/2064_prsn_KT8q7.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/1c/06/2064_prsn_KT8q7.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/1c/06/2064_prsn_KT8q7.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/1c/06/2064_prsn_KT8q7.jpg"},"name":"新海誠","short_summary":"新海 诚（Makoto Shinkai，まこと しんかい，1973年2月9日－），男，居住在东京。日本长野县野泽北高等学校、日本中央大学文学部国文学专攻毕业。1996-2001年就职于Falcom游戏会社，目前自由职业，以制作个人动画为主。 \r\n\r\n《永远的Ys2》的OP动画对于Falcom玩家而言应该记忆犹新。绚丽的2D动画效果配合近乎完美的节奏感，给人以强烈的感官震撼。这就是新海诚在职F社5年间的代表作之一。 1996年，新海诚在大学结业后加入日本Falcom游戏会社（通常在相关仕事中以新津诚名义出现），负责程序、美工、动画与宣传影片制作。在职Falcom期间，新海氏开始了个人动画短片创作。包括1997年的黑白短片《遥远世界》（1分30秒）、1998年的3D短片《被包围的世界》（30秒）、1999-2000年的黑白短片《她和她的猫》（5分钟）。 2000年初夏，新海氏开始制作个人映像动画《星之声》。但由于工作的繁忙，导致《星之声》一度停滞不前。2001年5月，新海氏向Falcom提交辞职。之后《星之声》的制作步上正轨，2002年1月宣告完工，历时共计7个月。此外，新海氏也曾外注参与制作Minori游戏会社游戏《Bittersweet Fools》（2001）、《Wind·a breath of heart》（2002）片头动画。 2003年新海诚新作《云的彼端，约定的地方》（预定片长50分钟）。在背景设定与情节方面，与架空感十足的《星之声》相比更加的平稳自然。由田泽潮担任人设更是弥补了新海人设较苍白的缺陷。担任Minori游戏会社游戏《EF - the first tale》(2006)的动画监制(Animation Movie Director)。","career":["producer","seiyu"],"id":2064,"type":1,"locked":false},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/50/75/3903_prsn_0N07U.jpg?r=1478378135","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/50/75/3903_prsn_0N07U.jpg?r=1478378135","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/50/75/3903_prsn_0N07U.jpg?r=1478378135","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/50/75/3903_prsn_0N07U.jpg?r=1478378135"},"name":"鈴木千尋","short_summary":"日本の男性声優。山形県出身。血液型はA型。身長165cm、体重50kg。フリー、オフィスモノリス（業務提携）。星座はみずがめ座。干支はへび。","career":["artist","seiyu"],"id":3903,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":27785}],"detail":[{"birth_mon":null,"gender":"female","birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/04/5c/2766_crt_anidb.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/04/5c/2766_crt_anidb.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/04/5c/2766_crt_anidb.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/04/5c/2766_crt_anidb.jpg"},"summary":"","name":"長峰美加子","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"长峰美加子"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"k":"日文名","v":"長峰美加子"},{"k":"罗马字","v":"Nagamine Mikako"}]},{"key":"性别","value":"女"},{"key":"引用来源","value":"anidb.net"}],"stat":{"comments":2,"collects":19},"id":2766,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":"male","birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/71/be/27785_crt_uuuH8.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/71/be/27785_crt_uuuH8.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/71/be/27785_crt_uuuH8.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/71/be/27785_crt_uuuH8.jpg"},"summary":"","name":"寺尾昇","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"寺尾升"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"k":"英文名","v":"Terao Noboru"},{"k":"日文名","v":"寺尾 昇"},{"k":"纯假名","v":"てらお のぼる"},{"k":"罗马字","v":"Terao Noboru"}]},{"key":"性别","value":"男"},{"key":"引用来源","value":"http://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/ほしのこえ"}],"stat":{"comments":4,"collects":6},"id":27785,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false}]}